- Oh...

195
00:08:32,950 --> 00:08:34,780
Hey.

196
00:08:35,820 --> 00:08:37,050
Hey!

197
00:08:37,150 --> 00:08:39,060
Hey.

198
00:08:39,150 --> 00:08:41,820
Ừ, kiểu như cái gì vậy?

199
00:08:41,920 --> 00:08:42,930
Thôi nào anh bạn.
Chuyện gì vậy?

200
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:44,660
- Hey, yeah.
